metadata.name: 7 Songs at 7 Stages
metadata.description:
This ERC-1155 token is the digital collectible version of Terra Naomi's live album "7 Songs at 7 Stages," recorded by MG O'Shea during a live performance at Atlanta's 7 Stages Theatre on August 26, 2018. 

This special NFT version of the live album includes a recording of unreleased song "Bleed For You." 

This NFT will render as a PLAYABLE ALBUM on platforms that support HTML-based NFTs (such as OpenSea) once minted. 

-----

Interactive Player Browser Link: https://cdn.warpsound.ai/ipfs/QmVYW5vHaV322Kvp2So5ErngP1PrDUneYqo4e9TNygAGSn?playlist-url=https://gateway.pinata.cloud/ipfs/QmR78MdVLz3oN9eDvyHJVT1hHLdo6Z6Av3ZXkvX6eQSTy9

Track Listing:

You For Me  
Everything
